/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hostthe July 26-Aug 11 Gamesis\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"the record\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris' main outlays have included just three major builds - its Olympics Village expected to cost about \\u20ac1.5 billion, the Aquatics Centre at \\u20ac175 million and a \\u20ac138 million badminton and gymnastics arena.\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 947, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999272404, \"rank\": 7.261515500995143e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just three major builds\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"its Olympics Village\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\u20ac138 million badminton and gymnastics arena\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not expect the Games to weigh significantly on French public-sector entities, including Paris and the central government,\\\" said S&P, which specialises in assessing creditworthiness.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.67359425087961, \"rank\": 0.4816048039209548, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1248, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999272404, \"rank\": 7.261515500995143e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1288, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso